race.comment: The scratching of a couple of the better chances now leaves a strong match between SHARE THE STARS and POWERING AWAY, SHARE THE STARS (11) showed ability in first campaign and finished off in town with a fifth over 1400m. This much easier and expected to go close fresh. POWERING AWAY (2) has placed at both starts so far, running on well at each. Will spot a start but on what he's shown so far will be powering home late. THE ADIGE (5) resumes from a long spell after finishing fifth over 1300m on a wet track over the winter. Has upside and sharpened with two trials should run well while fresh.  BRUTIFY (7) is a 10 start maiden but edging towards a win and just missed last time. Among the chances again.
